data.description:
LAKE EUCHA VIEW at this must see home with separate Guest house! 
Enjoy the open living space with 2 bedrooms/2 bathes. Upstairs loft to use for guest , game room or second living area.This great home offers a covered porch,Fenced yard, and privacy at the end of the road! 
The Guest house is full open concept, complete with kitchen area, bath,living room and bedroom area.
The shop is 24x35 for all your lake toys!
